{
  "texts": [
    "Against this backdrop, this study aims to develop a Transformer-based multidimensional feedback system that addresses the shortcomings of current technologies and better meets the needs of English writing instruction.",
    "The following sections outline the system's research and development process, as well as its practical applications.",
    "This study's comparison with recent literature underscores its unique position and practical value.",
    "Unlike the multidimensional writing assessment framework based on large language models (LLMs) proposed by Tang et al. (2024) 24, this system utilizes the Transformer's self-attention mechanism to provide more detailed feedback.",
    "It not only addresses basic dimensions such as grammatical accuracy but also introduces the Hierarchical Attention Model, which jointly models sentence-and paragraph-level features."
  ]
}